Step 1: Create github account
Step 2: Create a repositary in github site (initialize it by creating readme file - select that option)
Step 3: After installing git in eclipse, add the repository which is created in github site
Step 4: Create projects and programs as usual and select team -> shareit to github & provide the repository details.
Step 5: Commit the repository (Unsaved changes -> Right click add index)

